+Discourse .GIF to .MP4
+======================
+
+Installation
+------------
+
+Simply clone this Git repository in the `plugins` folder of your Discourse installation.
+
+Dependencies
+------------
+
+* ffmpeg
+
+Why MP4?
+--------
+
+#### Advantages
+
+* Smaller size
+* Saves bandwidth
+* Better quality
+* Support for audio (irrelevant in this case anyway)
+
+#### Disadvantages
+* Requires a modern browser
